vijf maanden in nederland!
bedankt iedereen die me geholpen jeeft in deze vijf maanden
vooral klas 4G, mijn volleybal team en mijn familie
ik heb een leuke tijd hier
------------------
this five months are really a whole new experience for me
i have learnt a lot which i cant learn in the textbook
and also i made many many many new friends
Although sometimes I also feel sad or down, but I know after the sadness, I learn from it and make me growth.

In these 5 months, many people also told me that 'everyone is perfect in their own way'
I really like this sentence and also because of this, I tried to do something I want to do, no matter how others think
I tried something new is because I want to get something i dont have now.
For example, I have started a new project last week. I signed up for another private instagram account and tried to get some idea from my daily life and share how I feel, how I thought to others
maybe the photos are not perfect, but i enjoyed the time to make these stuff and maybe the photos really can make other happy and laugh hahaha
anyway I believe that 5 months later, when I have to leave, I will become a brand new Samuel Wong
I dont know how I changed at last, but I only know that I really enjoy being the one I really want to be.
(P.S. @samueljustforfun my private account, i will try to accept more followers if i want or any other reason haha)
